definition: Gongshu district of Hangzhou city 杭州市[Hang2 zhou1 shi4], Zhejiang
to cup one's hands in salute/to surround/to arch/to dig earth with the snout/arched

sentences.english: This project is at the southern end of Gongchen Bridge in north Gongshu, which is the south terminal of Jing-Hang Canal.
sentences.chinese: 該項目位於拱墅區北部拱宸橋南，是京杭運河的南端。

sentences.english: The Gongshu District also planned to allot 100 million yuan to further improve the conditions of schools.
sentences.chinese: 拱墅區政府還計劃撥款一億元用來推進學校建設。
